\c 13
\s Umfanekiso womhlanyeli
\p
\v 1 Kwathi ngalolosuku uJesu waphuma endlini\x + 9.28. 13.36.\x* wahlala phansi elwandle\x + Mark. 4.1-12.\x*.
\v 2 Kwasekubuthana kuye amaxuku amakhulu\x + Luka 8.4-10.\x*, waze wangena\x + Luka 5.3.\x* emkhunjini wahlala phansi; lexuku lonke lema ekhunjini\x + Mark. 3.9.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Wasekhuluma labo izinto ezinengi ngemifanekiso, esithi: Khangelani, kwaphuma umhlanyeli ukuyahlanyela.
\v 4 Kwathi ekuhlanyeleni kwakhe, enye \add inhlanyelo\add* yawela eceleni kwendlela; kwasekufika inyoni, zayidla zayiqeda.
\v 5 Kodwa enye yawela emhlabathini olamatshe, lapho eyayingelamhlabathi omnengi khona; futhi yahle yamila, ngoba kwakungelakutshona komhlabathi;
\v 6 kwathi ekuphumeni kwelanga yahangulwa; njalo ngoba yayingelampande yabuna.
\v 7 Kodwa enye yawela emeveni; ameva asekhula ayiminyanisa\x + Jer. 4.3.\x*.
\v 8 Kodwa enye yawela emhlabathini omuhle, yathela isithelo\x + Joha. 15.5.\x*, enye ikhulu, lenye amatshumi ayisithupha, lenye amatshumi amathathu\x + Gen. 26.12.\x*.
\v 9 Olendlebe zokuzwa, akezwe\x + 11.15.\x*.
\s Umsebenzi wemifanekiso
\p
\v 10 Kwasekufika abafundi bathi kuye: Ukhulumelani kubo ngemifanekiso?
\v 11 Wasephendula wathi kubo: Ngoba kuphiwe kini\x + 19.11. 11.25. 1 Kor. 2.10. 1 Joha. 2.27.\x* ukwazi imfihlo zombuso wamazulu, kodwa bona kabakunikwanga.
\v 12 Ngoba loba ngubani olakho uzaphiwa, abe lokwengezelelweyo; kodwa lowo ongelakho, uzakwemukwa\x + 25.29. Mark. 4.25. Luka 8.18; 19.26. Joha. 15.2.\x* lalokho alakho\x + Luka 8.18.\x*.
\v 13 Ngakho ngikhuluma labo ngemifanekiso, ngoba bebona kababoni, njalo besizwa kabezwa, futhi kabaqedisisi.
\v 14 Kubo besekugcwaliseka isiprofetho sikaIsaya, esithi: Ukuzwa lizakuzwa, kodwa kalisoze liqedisise; lokubona lizabona, kodwa kalisoze libonisise;
\v 15 ngoba inhliziyo yalababantu seyaba lukhuni\x + Isa. 6.9,10. Joha. 12.40. Seb. 28.26,27. Dute. 29.4. Isa. 43.8. Jer. 5.21. Hez. 12.2. Roma 11.8. 2 Kor. 3.14; 4.4.\x*, njalo bezwa kanzima ngendlebe, lamehlo abo bawacimezile; hlezi \add loba nini\add* babone ngamehlo, njalo bezwe ngendlebe, futhi baqedisise ngenhliziyo\x + Heb. 5.11.\x*, njalo baphenduke, besengibasilisa\x + Luka 22.32.\x*.
\v 16 Kodwa abusisiwe amehlo enu\x + 13.16,17, Luka 10.23,24.\x*, ngoba ayabona; lendlebe zenu, ngoba ziyezwa\x + 16.17. Joha. 20.29.\x*.
\v 17 Ngoba ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Abaprofethi labalungileyo abanengi babethanda ukubona izinto elizibonayo, kodwa kaba\add zi\add*bonanga; lokuzwa izinto elizizwayo kodwa kaba\add zi\add*zwanga\x + Heb. 11.13. 1 Pet. 1.10,11. Joha. 8.56.\x*.
\s Ukuchasiswa komfanekiso womhlanyeli
\p
\v 18 Ngakho lina zwanini umfanekiso womhlanyeli\x + Mark. 4.13-20. Luka 8.11-15.\x*.
\v 19 Kuthi wonke ozwayo ilizwi lombuso kodwa engaqedisisi\x + 4.23; 8.12. 13.38.\x*, omubi afike, ahluthune okuhlanyelwe enhliziyweni yakhe. Lo nguye ohlanyelwe eceleni kwendlela\x + 13.38. 6.13. Joha. 17.15. Efe. 6.16. 2 Thes. 3.3. 1 Joha. 2.13,14; 3.12; 5.18,19.\x*.
\v 20 Kodwa ohlanyelwe emhlabathini olamatshe, nguye olizwayo ilizwi, ahle alemukele\x + Mark. 1.30. Mat. 13.21.\x* ngentokozo;
\v 21 kodwa kalampande phakathi kwakhe\x + Isa. 58.2. Hez. 33.31,32. Mark. 6.20. Joha. 5.35.\x*, kodwa uhlala isikhathi; kuthi sekufika inkathazo kumbe ukuzingelwa ngenxa yelizwi\x + Mark. 4.17. 2 Kor. 4.18. Heb. 11.25.\x*, ahle\x + Mark. 6.25. Luka 17.7; 21.9. Mat. 13.20.\x* akhubeke\x + 11.6. 2 Tim. 1.15.\x*.
\v 22 Lohlanyelwe emeveni, nguye olizwayo ilizwi, kodwa impisekelo yalumhlaba lenkohliso\x + 2 Tim. 4.10.\x* yenotho kuyaliminyanisa ilizwi, futhi lingabi lesithelo\x + 19.23.\x*.
\v 23 Kodwa ohlanyelwe emhlabathini omuhle, nguye olizwayo ilizwi aliqedisise; isibili athele izithelo, aveze, omunye ikhulu, lomunye amatshumi ayisithupha, lomunye amatshumi amathathu.
\s Umfanekiso womfaba, lowemasitedi, lowemvubelo
\p
\v 24 Wabeka phambi kwabo omunye umfanekiso, esithi: Umbuso wamazulu ufananiswa lomuntu owahlanyela inhlanyelo enhle ensimini yakhe.
\v 25 Kodwa abantu besalele, kwafika isitha sakhe sahlanyela umfaba phakathi kwamabele, sahamba.
\v 26 Kodwa kwathi selumilile usungulo lwathela isithelo, lomfaba wasubonakala.
\v 27 Zasezisondela inceku zomninimuzi zathi kuye: Nkosi, kawuhlanyelanga yini inhlanyelo enhle ensimini yakho? Pho iwuthethe ngaphi umfaba?
\v 28 Wasesithi kuzo: Umuntu oyisitha ukwenzile lokhu. Inceku zasezisithi kuye: Uthanda ukuthi siyewubutha yini?
\v 29 Kodwa wathi: Hatshi, hlezi, ekubutheni kwenu umfaba, lisiphune amabele kanye lawo.
\v 30 Yekelani kukhule kokubili ndawonye kuze kube yisivuno; langesikhathi sokuvuna ngizakuthi kwabavunayo: Buthani kuqala umfaba, liwubophe izinyanda ukuze liwutshise\x + Mark. 4.26-29. Mat. 13.37-42.\x*; kodwa amabele liwabuthele esiphaleni sami\x + 3.12.\x*.
\p
\v 31 Wasebabekela omunye umfanekiso, esithi: Umbuso wamazulu\x + 13.31,32, Mark. 4.30-32. Luka 13.18,19.\x* unjengohlamvu lwemasitedi, aluthatha umuntu waluhlanyela ensimini yakhe;
\v 32 lona kambe luncinyane kulazo zonke inhlamvu; kodwa nxa selukhulile\x + 17.20. Luka 17.6.\x*, lukhulu kulezilimo zonke, njalo luba yisihlahla\x + Mark. 4.32.\x*, kuze kufike inyoni zezulu, zakhele engatsheni zaso\x + Hlab. 104.12.\x*.
\p
\v 33 Wabatshela omunye umfanekiso, \add wathi\add*: Umbuso wamazulu unjengemvubelo\x + Luka 13.20,21.\x*, ayithathayo owesifazana wayifaka emagokokweni amathathu empuphu, kwaze kwabila konke\x + Gen. 18.6. Hlu. 6.19. 1 Sam. 1.24.\x*.
\p
\v 34 Lezizinto zonke uJesu wazikhuluma emaxukwini ngemifanekiso, futhi ngaphandle komfanekiso kakhulumanga kubo;
\v 35 ukuze kugcwaliseke okwakhulunywa ngumprofethi\x + Mark. 4.33,34.\x*, esithi: Ngizavula umlomo wami ngemifanekiso\x + Hlab. 78.2.\x*, ngizaveza izinto ebezifihlakele\x + Roma 16.25,26.\x* kusukela ekusekelweni komhlaba\x + 25.34. Luka 11.50. Heb. 4.3; 9.26. Isam. 13.8; 17.8. Joha. 17.24. 1 Pet. 1.20.\x*.
\p
\v 36 Kwathi uJesu esewayekele amaxuku ahamba wangena endlini\x + 13.1.\x*; basebesondela kuye abafundi bakhe, besithi: Sichasisele umfanekiso womfaba ensimini\x + 13.24-30.\x*.
\v 37 Wasephendula wathi kubo: Ohlanyela inhlanyelo enhle yiNdodana yomuntu;
\v 38 lensimu ngumhlaba\x + Mark. 16.15,20. Kol. 1.6.\x*; lenhlanyelo enhle, yona ingabantwana bombuso\x + 8.12. 13.43.\x*; kodwa umfaba ungabantwana bomubi\x + Joha. 8.44. Seb. 13.10. 1 Joha. 3.8,10.\x*;
\v 39 lesitha esawuhlanyelayo ngudiyabhola\x + 13.19.\x*; lesivuno siyikuphela kwesikhathi\x + Jow. 3.13. Isam. 14.15.\x*; labavunayo bazingilosi.
\v 40 Ngakho-ke njengalokhu umfaba uyabuthwa utshiswe emlilweni\x + 13.40,49. 24.3; 28.20. Heb. 9.26. Dan. 12.13.\x*, kuzakuba njalo ekupheleni kwalesisikhathi\x + 13.40,49. 24.3; 28.20. Heb. 9.26. Dan. 12.13.\x*.
\v 41 INdodana yomuntu izathuma ingilosi zayo, besezibutha zikhuphe embusweni wayo konke okukhubekisayo lalabo abenza okubi\x + 24.31.\x*,
\v 42 besezibaphosela\x + 13.50. 3.12. Isam. 9.2; 19.20; 20.10.\x* esithandweni somlilo\x + 13.50.\x*; lapho kuzakuba khona ukukhala lokugedla amazinyo\x + 8.12.\x*.
\v 43 Khona abalungileyo bezakhanya njengelanga\x + Zaga 4.18. Dan. 12.3.\x* embusweni kaYise\x + 26.29. 13.38.\x*. Olendlebe zokuzwa akezwe\x + 13.9. 11.15.\x*.
\s Umfanekiso wenotho, lowamangqongqo aligugu lowembule
\p
\v 44 Futhi umbuso wamazulu unjengempahla eligugu efihliweyo ensimini, okuthi umuntu eseyificile wa\add yi\add*fihla\x + Zaga 2.4.\x*; entokozweni yakhe uyahamba, athengise konke alakho\x + 13.46. Fil. 3.7,8.\x*, athenge leyonsimu\x + 13.46. Isa. 55.1. Isam. 3.18.\x*.
\p
\v 45 Futhi umbuso wamazulu unjengomuntu ongumthengi odinga \w amapharele\w** amahle;
\v 46 esethole elinye ipharele eliligugu kakhulu\x + Jobe 28.18. Zaga 3.15; 8.11.\x*, wasuka wathengisa konke alakho\x + 13.46. Fil. 3.7,8.\x*, walithenga\x + 13.46. Isa. 55.1. Isam. 3.18.\x*.
\p
\v 47 Futhi umbuso wamazulu unjengembule elaphoswa olwandle\x + 4.19.\x*, laselibutha zonke inhlobo;
\v 48 lona, lithe seligcwele, balidonsela ekhunjini, bahlala phansi, babuthela ezilungileyo ezitsheni, kodwa ezimbi bazilahlela ngaphandle\x + 13.46. Isa. 55.1. Isam. 3.18.\x*.
\v 49 Kuzakuba njalo ekupheleni kwesikhathi\x + 13.39.\x*; ingilosi zizaphuma, zehlukanise ababi zibasuse phakathi kwabalungileyo\x + 25.32.\x*,
\v 50 besezibaphosela esithandweni somlilo; lapho kuzakuba khona ukukhala lokugedla amazinyo\x + 13.42.\x*.
\p
\v 51 UJesu wathi kubo: Seliziqedisisile zonke lezizinto yini? Bathi kuye: Yebo, Nkosi\x + Joha. 10.6.\x*.
\v 52 Wasesithi kubo: Ngakho wonke umbhali\x + 23.34.\x* ofundiselwe umbuso wamazulu unjengomuntu ongumninimuzi, okhupha empahleni yakhe eligugu\x + 28.19.\x* okutsha lokudala.
\s UJesu udelelwa emzini wakibo
\p
\v 53 Kwasekusithi uJesu eseqedile limifanekiso, wasuka lapho.
\v 54 Wathi esefikile\x + Mark. 6.1-6. Luka 4.16-30.\x* emzini wakibo\x + 2.23. Luka 4.23.\x* wabafundisa esinagogeni labo\x + 26.55.\x*, baze bamangala bathi: Ivela ngaphi kuyenalo linhlakanipho\x + 7.28.\x* lalimisebenzi yamandla\x + 7.22; 11.20,21,23; 14.2. 13.58.\x*?
\v 55 Lo kayisiyo yini\x + Luka 3.23; 4.22. Joha. 6.42.\x* indodana yombazi? Unina kathiwa nguMariya yini\x + Mark. 6.3.\x*, labafowabo\x + 12.46.\x* oJakobe loJose loSimoni loJudasi?
\v 56 Labodadewabo kabakho yini bonke kithi? Pho, zivela ngaphi zonke lezizinto kuye\x + 27.56. Mark. 15.40. Gal. 1.19.\x*?
\v 57 Basebekhubeka ngaye\x + 11.6.\x*. Kodwa uJesu wathi kubo: Umprofethi kasweli ukudunyiswa ngaphandle kwelizweni lakibo lendlini yakwabo\x + Luka 4.24. Joha. 4.44. Jer. 11.21; 12.6.\x*.
\v 58 Njalo kenzanga lapho imisebenzi yamandla eminengi\x + Mark. 6.5,6. Luka 4.23-27.\x*, ngenxa yokungakholwa kwabo\x + Mark. 9.23.\x*.